<h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hello [% user.first_name || user.username || 'there' %],</p>

<p>Thank you for registering with [% sitename || 'Comserv' %]. To complete your registration, please enter the verification code below:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">Your verification code is:</p>
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #007bff;">[% code %]</p>
</div>

<p>This code will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>

<p>If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The [% sitename || 'Comserv' %] Team</p>
